  "detailed_description": "<strong>Gravitia is a unique adventure game that utilizes gravity to escape a mysterious world.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/c4c482947b65e726d119743abb00738d.poster.avif?t=1769133434\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/c4c482947b65e726d119743abb00738d.webm?t=1769133434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/c4c482947b65e726d119743abb00738d.mp4?t=1769133434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/4a7e0852db9070ffbaceec8ab7a7e095.webp?t=1769133434\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br>The gun creates a gravity field centered on the point of impact, which attracts the environment and objects except for gravity bullets. <br>This allows you to move objects that are out of reach or move walls that are in your way to move forward. <br>Try this unique interaction that defies the laws of nature for a different experience.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/49378d30220b613d3b57cf0cb0265489.webp?t=1769133434\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br>It is unclear where this mysterious place is located and how it came to be. <br>Explore the unknown and approach the secrets of the space as they unfold in the fog. As the fog slowly clears, you will gradually reach the secrets of the space.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Gravitia is a unique adventure game that utilizes gravity to escape a mysterious world.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/c4c482947b65e726d119743abb00738d.poster.avif?t=1769133434\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/c4c482947b65e726d119743abb00738d.webm?t=1769133434\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/c4c482947b65e726d119743abb00738d.mp4?t=1769133434\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/4a7e0852db9070ffbaceec8ab7a7e095.webp?t=1769133434\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br>The gun creates a gravity field centered on the point of impact, which attracts the environment and objects except for gravity bullets. <br>This allows you to move objects that are out of reach or move walls that are in your way to move forward. <br>Try this unique interaction that defies the laws of nature for a different experience.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2735690/extras/49378d30220b613d3b57cf0cb0265489.webp?t=1769133434\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br>It is unclear where this mysterious place is located and how it came to be. <br>Explore the unknown and approach the secrets of the space as they unfold in the fog. As the fog slowly clears, you will gradually reach the secrets of the space.",
